Package org.modelio.archimate.metamodel.relationships.structural

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Aggregation
    Aggregation vnull The aggregation relationship indicates that an element groups a number of other elements.
    Assignment
    Assignment vnull The assignment relationship links active structure elements with units of behavior that are performed by them, business actors with business roles that are fulfilled by them, locations with structure elements, and artifacts with nodes.
    Composition
    Composition vnull The composition relationship has been inspired by the composition relationship in UML class diagrams.
    Realization
    Realization vnull The realization relationship models that an entity plays a critical role in the creation, achievement, sustenance, or operation of a more abstract entity.
    StructuralRelationship
    StructuralRelationship vnull Structural relationships represent the 'static' coherence within an architecture.
